paragraph.content:
income and profits derived from the charter or rental of aircraft
                        provided that such charter or rental is incidental to the operation of
                        aircraft in international traffic;

subsection.def:
the term “international
                        traffic” means any transport by an aircraft except when the aircraft
                    is operated solely between places in the other Contracting Party;

subsection.content:
in the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region, for any year of assessment
                    beginning on or after 1st April in the calendar year in which this Article
                    enters into force;

in the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region, for any year of assessment
                    beginning on or after 1st April in the calendar year next following that in
                    which notice is given;
